{"tid":1562392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「願榮光歸香港」返回起點思考","createTime":"2019-09-12T03:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T06:22:58.000Z","uid":118910,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d2f14d42e94f486afdfad38c79a452b5451939","tid":1562392,"uid":118910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:54:35.000Z","msg":"呢個運動成功起風都係因為無大台<br />\n每個人都可以係軍師每個人都可以比意見<br />\n唔會有人騎劫<br />\n<br />\n我自己係廣場同大家一齊唱<br />\n真係好感動<br />\n好帶動到自己對香港呢個土地嘅歸屬感<br />\n係呢個咁亂嘅時間有一首歌可以做到呢樣野真係唔易<br />\n<br />\n今次有人突然一兩晚內洗版狂屌呢首歌<br />\n更有懷疑係熱普城係後面搞鬼<br />\n大家應該把持番無大台嘅道理<br />\n覺得啱就支持正皮推po<br />\n覺得做多咗/方向唔啱就負皮由佢沉"},{"pid":"0ec3368f3e9deb9ab50a75bdaa50be443c888665","tid":1562392,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"add3d7e6581b1fdd64130bacb5961eed188ae581","tid":1562392,"uid":55257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:59:59.000Z","msg":"其實純粹係首歌能夠鼓舞人心，都係一件好事，做瑜團結陣線係好重要，我唔會理邊個人作"},{"pid":"0f43a48b9a60c8c0a046afb9f716613647ae69ab","tid":1562392,"uid":118910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"add3d7e6581b1fdd64130bacb5961eed188ae581","tid":1562392,"uid":55257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re